blueprint.label: Starter Base
blueprint.description:
By bcwhite (v1.2)
Blue-science (optional) additions by @udim.

The constant combinators indicate what materials need to go on what lanes but they're only in the correct location if entering from the bottom and going "up".  If this is rotated, be sure the lanes are correct.

The "blue science" section won't be operational until silver ore is extracted from thermal water and processed into plates.
